headline: Square Financial Services, Inc. Launches 25 Squared Grant Initiative to Drive Community Development in Utah
summary: DISTRIBUTED-WORK-MODEL/OAKLAND, Calif., September 24, 2025--Square Financial Services, Inc., a Utah state-chartered industrial bank and an independently governed subsidiary of Block, Inc. (NYSE: XYZ), today opened applications for the 25 Squared Grant Initiative in partnership with the Community Foundation of Utah (CFU).
